auth_key_derivation_path.properties: private entry provides us future ability to regenerate AuthKey from Master Seed

authorizor.properties: Used to set the authorizing keys for each device

device_authorization.properties: Struct that proves a sucessfull handshake between two devices

key_meta.properties: private entry for NewKey registration which provides context and ability to regenerate from Master Seed.

key_registration.properties: Entry to register a any keys on DeepKey

keyset_root.properties: Root hash that would be used as an anchor

rules.properties: This is the rules that the agent sets for his DeepKey acc
